data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Great opportunity to own 2 homes on apx 9 acres in the hills of Willamina. Main home has large kitchen, wood stove & spacious living room. Newer roof, new dishwasher, water heater & updated floor insulation. Beautiful deck to enjoy the scenery. 2nd home is 5/2, 1782SF with hardship permit. Property is in forest deferral. Includes 36 x 40 shop & other small outbuildings. Buyer to do all due diligence on hardship permit & forest deferral. Close to OHV trails, hunting, fishing, and recreational activities.
